@azkoss 
Or, you can try 4.0.0-RC2. I can not get the detail of your issue, but we actually fix a bug about generatedKey, so you can give a try for 4.0.0.RC2

@terrymanu @KomachiSion I have gone through the feedback on the attached PR. From what I understand, letting `ShardingStrategy` decide what to do if `shardingValues` is empty or not contradicts the design of ShardingSphere.

Referring back to the sql examine feature, can you please explain a bit more in detail on what are you guys planning in that feature. Would want to understand if that helps my use case or not. 

Mentioning my use case again, I need some way to override the behaviour of full-routing when no sharding column is there in the SQL.

Please try 4.0.0-RC1 or RC2-SNAPSHOT.
There's known issue in 3.1.0 about LIMIT.
@lyy2002
